    To create adequate opportunities for the members of transgender and intersex community so that they can be empowered and uplifted.
    They will be a valuable addition to the nation's work force.

    <hr />

    <u>VISION</u>
    <br />
    To create a more inclusive society where transgender and intersex people are not looked down upon.

</body>
</html>

